<br/><br/>Cancellation of Services or account<br/>If you wish to cancel your YubeFit account, you can send an email of request to Admin@ActivEdge.sg. As the operation of cancelling your YubeFit account will prevent you from using YubeFit and Services, please proceed with caution. We will provide a form of cancellation to be return to us. We will process your request within a five (5) business days after you make the request. In order to protect the legitimate rights and interests of you or others, we will determine whether to support your cancellation request based on your use of YubeFit and Services by conducting account verification.<br/><br/>Language<br/>The Privacy Policy shall be prepared and executed in English and if translated into a language other than English for any purpose, the English version shall in all events prevail and be paramount in the event of any differences, questions or disputes concerning the meaning, form, validity, or interpretation of this.<br/><br/>Our Contact Details<br/>ASPL and its subsidiaries are committed to protecting your personal data. If you have questions or comments about ASPL’s administration of personal data relating to YubeFit App, please contact us.<br/><br/></p></body></html>